{
  "video_id": "5RRyX9mI5Lw",
  "title": "Mass media | Society and Culture | MCAT | Khan Academy",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 1398.0,
      "end_time": 2815.0,
      "text": "- [Voiceover] What exactly\r\nare we talking about"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 2815.0,
      "end_time": 4916.0,
      "text": "when we talk about mass media?"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 4916.0,
      "end_time": 7632.0,
      "text": "Well, we're talking about the\r\ndissemination of information,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 7632.0,
      "end_time": 10859.0,
      "text": "or how information is\r\ntransmitted within a culture."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 10859.0,
      "end_time": 12334.0,
      "text": "And this can include print media,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 12334.0,
      "end_time": 14899.0,
      "text": "like books, newspapers, and magazines,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 14899.0,
      "end_time": 15957.0,
      "text": "as well as digital media,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 15957.0,
      "end_time": 19521.0,
      "text": "like TV, movies, radio, and the internet."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 19521.0,
      "end_time": 21401.0,
      "text": "Exactly how this media is consumed"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 21401.0,
      "end_time": 23631.0,
      "text": "changes across cultures and age groups."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 23631.0,
      "end_time": 26139.0,
      "text": "For example, my grandmother\r\ngets a lot of her information"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 26139.0,
      "end_time": 29040.0,
      "text": "about current events\r\nthrough TV and newspapers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 29040.0,
      "end_time": 31615.0,
      "text": "but I primarily get\r\nthis information online."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 32868.0,
      "end_time": 34261.0,
      "text": "And when we look at mass media,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 34261.0,
      "end_time": 36293.0,
      "text": "we can look at the role\r\nit plays in our society"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 36293.0,
      "end_time": 39066.0,
      "text": "through different\r\nsociological perspectives."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 39601.0,
      "end_time": 41579.0,
      "text": "So according to the functionalist view,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 41579.0,
      "end_time": 43797.0,
      "text": "one of the most important\r\nfunctions of mass media"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 43797.0,
      "end_time": 46060.0,
      "text": "is to provide entertainment."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 46060.0,
      "end_time": 48605.0,
      "text": "So it's meant to occupy our leisure time."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 49133.0,
      "end_time": 51478.0,
      "text": "But the functionalist view\r\nalso says that mass media"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 51478.0,
      "end_time": 54137.0,
      "text": "can also act as an agent of socialization"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 54137.0,
      "end_time": 56578.0,
      "text": "and an enforcer of social norms."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 57164.0,
      "end_time": 59764.0,
      "text": "It presents a standardized view of society"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 59764.0,
      "end_time": 61506.0,
      "text": "and provides a collective experience"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 61506.0,
      "end_time": 63673.0,
      "text": "for members of that society."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 63673.0,
      "end_time": 65414.0,
      "text": "Think about the shared experience"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 65414.0,
      "end_time": 67794.0,
      "text": "of watching the Olympics on television,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 67794.0,
      "end_time": 69094.0,
      "text": "or being with a group of people"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 69094.0,
      "end_time": 71372.0,
      "text": "to see a movie on opening night."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 72004.0,
      "end_time": 75035.0,
      "text": "Mass media also functions\r\nto bring people together."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 75035.0,
      "end_time": 77240.0,
      "text": "And there are entire\r\ninternet-based communities"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 77240.0,
      "end_time": 78680.0,
      "text": "that are focused on things like"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 78680.0,
      "end_time": 80874.0,
      "text": "LGBT rights or childcare,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 80874.0,
      "end_time": 84418.0,
      "text": "or fans of music groups that\r\nsing songs about Harry Potter."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 85387.0,
      "end_time": 87140.0,
      "text": "But mass media can also tell us"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 87140.0,
      "end_time": 89067.0,
      "text": "about what society expects of us"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 89067.0,
      "end_time": 91568.0,
      "text": "through what it rewards and punishes."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 91568.0,
      "end_time": 92461.0,
      "text": "So when we hear something about"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 92461.0,
      "end_time": 94683.0,
      "text": "criminal behavior from mass media,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 94683.0,
      "end_time": 96146.0,
      "text": "it is often talked about in terms of"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 96146.0,
      "end_time": 98270.0,
      "text": "bringing criminals to justice."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 98270.0,
      "end_time": 100325.0,
      "text": "Which reinforces the idea\r\nthat criminal behaviors"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 100325.0,
      "end_time": 102984.0,
      "text": "are bad and should be avoided."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 102984.0,
      "end_time": 106479.0,
      "text": "However, the media can\r\nsometimes also glorify behaviors"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 106479.0,
      "end_time": 108912.0,
      "text": "that society as a whole\r\nwould deem to be wrong."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 108912.0,
      "end_time": 111283.0,
      "text": "Things like intense physical violence."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 112926.0,
      "end_time": 114492.0,
      "text": "Mass media also functions"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 114492.0,
      "end_time": 116989.0,
      "text": "as a promoter of consumer culture."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 116989.0,
      "end_time": 119171.0,
      "text": "At the turn of the century,\r\nthe average U.S. child"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 119171.0,
      "end_time": 123107.0,
      "text": "saw 20,000 commercials a year on TV."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 123107.0,
      "end_time": 125023.0,
      "text": "And that doesn't include ads on the radio"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 125023.0,
      "end_time": 127344.0,
      "text": "or billboards or signs in front of stores"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 127344.0,
      "end_time": 129748.0,
      "text": "announcing 50% off sales."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 129747.99999999999,
      "end_time": 131746.0,
      "text": "And it's only increased from there."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 132449.0,
      "end_time": 134736.0,
      "text": "And it's not necessarily\r\nclear what kind of an impact"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 134736.0,
      "end_time": 136932.0,
      "text": "this might have on the next generation."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 138330.0,
      "end_time": 140002.0,
      "text": "The conflict view focuses on"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 140002.0,
      "end_time": 141941.0,
      "text": "how the media reflects and portrays,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 141941.0,
      "end_time": 143949.0,
      "text": "and may even exacerbate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 143949.0,
      "end_time": 146533.0,
      "text": "divisions that exist within our society."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 147026.0,
      "end_time": 149766.0,
      "text": "Like divisions based on\r\nrace, ethnicity, gender,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 149766.0,
      "end_time": 151207.0,
      "text": "or social class."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 152293.0,
      "end_time": 154789.0,
      "text": "Conflict theory uses the term gatekeeping"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 154789.0,
      "end_time": 156252.0,
      "text": "to describe the process by which"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 156252.0,
      "end_time": 158898.0,
      "text": "a small number of people and corporations"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 158898.0,
      "end_time": 161865.0,
      "text": "control what material is\r\nbeing presented on the media."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 162451.0,
      "end_time": 164552.0,
      "text": "It describes how information,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 164552.0,
      "end_time": 166955.0,
      "text": "so things that appear in our newspapers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 166955.0,
      "end_time": 169208.0,
      "text": "the stories that are made into movies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 169208.0,
      "end_time": 171738.0,
      "text": "what TV shows are turned into pilots,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 171738.0,
      "end_time": 174396.0,
      "text": "it describes how these things\r\nmove through a series of gates"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 174396.0,
      "end_time": 176408.0,
      "text": "before they can reach the public."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 176959.0,
      "end_time": 178538.0,
      "text": "In some countries, this\r\nmight be controlled"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 178538.0,
      "end_time": 180442.0,
      "text": "primarily by the government."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 180442.0,
      "end_time": 182209.0,
      "text": "But for others, it's decided primarily"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 182209.0,
      "end_time": 184515.0,
      "text": "by large media corporations."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 186030.0,
      "end_time": 187864.0,
      "text": "Gatekeeping can also\r\nhave more of an effect"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 187864.0,
      "end_time": 189695.0,
      "text": "on some media than others."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 189695.0,
      "end_time": 191854.0,
      "text": "For example, a lot of control is put on"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 191854.0,
      "end_time": 193758.0,
      "text": "what big-budget movies are made,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 193758.0,
      "end_time": 195372.0,
      "text": "but there is very little overhead control"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 195372.0,
      "end_time": 197278.0,
      "text": "of what gets posted online."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 197980.0,
      "end_time": 199407.0,
      "text": "The conflict theory also describes"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 199407.0,
      "end_time": 202996.0,
      "text": "how mass media often reflects\r\nthe dominant ideology."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 202996.0,
      "end_time": 205673.0,
      "text": "Giving time and space, or privileging,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 205673.0,
      "end_time": 208750.0,
      "text": "certain social, economical,\r\nand political interests,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 208750.0,
      "end_time": 211516.0,
      "text": "while sometimes actively\r\nlimiting other views."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 212415.0,
      "end_time": 213773.0,
      "text": "The people who make the choices about"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 213773.0,
      "end_time": 216594.0,
      "text": "what media is produced, the gatekeepers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 216594.0,
      "end_time": 219153.0,
      "text": "are predominantly white,\r\nmale, and wealthy."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 219153.0,
      "end_time": 221475.0,
      "text": "And as a result, stories\r\nrepresenting the views"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 221475.0,
      "end_time": 224900.0,
      "text": "of racial minority groups,\r\nwomen, LGBT individuals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 224900.0,
      "end_time": 228713.0,
      "text": "and working class people are\r\ntypically underrepresented."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 229195.0,
      "end_time": 231803.0,
      "text": "And because of this divide,\r\nportrayals of minority groups"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 231803.0,
      "end_time": 233580.0,
      "text": "can often be stereotyped,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 233580.0,
      "end_time": 236005.0,
      "text": "or guided by unrealistic generalizations"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 236005.0,
      "end_time": 238313.0,
      "text": "about a certain group of people."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 238313.0,
      "end_time": 240495.0,
      "text": "And while some corporations\r\nhave taken the steps"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 240495.0,
      "end_time": 242155.0,
      "text": "to try to improve this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 242155.0,
      "end_time": 244697.0,
      "text": "they sometimes take it\r\nin the wrong direction,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 244697.0,
      "end_time": 247922.0,
      "text": "which results in tokenism\r\ninstead of actual diversity."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 247922.0,
      "end_time": 250104.0,
      "text": "Or cases where a single minority member"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 250104.0,
      "end_time": 252101.0,
      "text": "is added to a TV show or movie"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 252101.0,
      "end_time": 254518.0,
      "text": "as a stand-in for that entire group."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 255743.0,
      "end_time": 257867.0,
      "text": "Feminist theory's\r\nunderstanding of mass media"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 257867.00000000003,
      "end_time": 260399.00000000003,
      "text": "is similar to what we would\r\nsee in conflict theory"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 260399.0,
      "end_time": 263022.0,
      "text": "in that it also holds that\r\nmass media stereotypes"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 263022.0,
      "end_time": 266542.0,
      "text": "and misrepresents society\r\ntowards the dominant ideology."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 267012.0,
      "end_time": 269357.0,
      "text": "Specifically, it focuses\r\non the way that messages"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 269357.0,
      "end_time": 272068.0,
      "text": "about men and women are\r\nrepresented in the media."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 272770.0,
      "end_time": 273931.0,
      "text": "It notes that women are often"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 273931.0,
      "end_time": 276369.0,
      "text": "underrepresented in media content,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 276369.0,
      "end_time": 278273.0,
      "text": "that men are often considered normal"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 278273.0,
      "end_time": 280711.0,
      "text": "while women are considered to be other."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 280711.0,
      "end_time": 282510.0,
      "text": "Think about ads for products."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 282510.0,
      "end_time": 285552.0,
      "text": "We have razors and razors for women."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 285552.0,
      "end_time": 287709.0,
      "text": "Pens and pens for her."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 288479.0,
      "end_time": 289794.0,
      "text": "Depictions of men and women"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 289794.0,
      "end_time": 291965.0,
      "text": "are often highly stereotyped,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 291965.0,
      "end_time": 293567.0,
      "text": "enforcing strict gender roles"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 293567.0,
      "end_time": 295741.0,
      "text": "and emphasizing traditional sex roles."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 296338.0,
      "end_time": 298394.0,
      "text": "So women are more often\r\nportrayed as victims"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 298394.0,
      "end_time": 300297.0,
      "text": "and men as aggressors."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 300297.0,
      "end_time": 302074.0,
      "text": "And women are much more\r\nlikely to be depicted"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 302074.0,
      "end_time": 304639.0,
      "text": "as shallow or being obsessed with looks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 304639.0,
      "end_time": 305951.0,
      "text": "which also makes it more likely"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 305951.0,
      "end_time": 308474.0,
      "text": "that they'll be sexualized\r\nand objectified."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 309036.0,
      "end_time": 310441.0,
      "text": "The interactionist perspective"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 310441.0,
      "end_time": 312565.0,
      "text": "looks at mass media on the micro level"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 312565.0,
      "end_time": 314916.0,
      "text": "to see how it shapes day to day behavior."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 315677.0,
      "end_time": 317836.0,
      "text": "It looks at how mass media blurs the line"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 317836.0,
      "end_time": 320292.0,
      "text": "between solitary and group activities."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 320843.0,
      "end_time": 323254.0,
      "text": "So think of the act of seeing a movie."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 323254.0,
      "end_time": 325333.0,
      "text": "You may be watching it with other people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 325333.0,
      "end_time": 328873.0,
      "text": "but because of societal\r\nnorms or even theater rules,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 328873.0,
      "end_time": 331451.0,
      "text": "you are actually forbidden\r\nfrom talking about the movie"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 331451.0,
      "end_time": 333194.0,
      "text": "with the people you're with."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 334325.0,
      "end_time": 335603.0,
      "text": "It also looks at the fact"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 335603.0,
      "end_time": 337739.0,
      "text": "that how we connect with\r\nother people using media"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 337739.0,
      "end_time": 339825.0,
      "text": "tends to change over time."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 339825.0,
      "end_time": 341075.0,
      "text": "So whereas before I might have called"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 341075.0,
      "end_time": 343037.0,
      "text": "my grandparents to keep\r\nin touch with them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 343037.0,
      "end_time": 345092.0,
      "text": "now I can talk with them via email,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 345092.0,
      "end_time": 346766.0,
      "text": "or even text message."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 347619.0,
      "end_time": 349418.0,
      "text": "The rate at which people\r\nmeet romantic partners"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 349418.0,
      "end_time": 351636.0,
      "text": "online has also increased,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 351636.0,
      "end_time": 353261.0,
      "text": "which is something that\r\nprobably would have seemed"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 353261.0,
      "end_time": 356704.0,
      "text": "very confusing to just a\r\nfew generations before ours."
    }
  ]
